ched with its q  product release designed to help nonprofits easily use technology for all their fundraising needs the release enables customers to access fundraising events communication and marketing solutions as well as reporting tools all in one single hub in recent industry surveys nonprofit organizations voice that they are continually seeking ways to consolidate their many technology solutions to more efficiently support their daytoday needs because of this mobilecause consolidates more than twentyfive fundraising donor communication event support and payment processing point solutions into a single platform making it more time and costefficient to raise money as well as provide a consistent donor experience “gone are the days of multiple logins inconsistent donor records and file sharing between countless nonprofit fundraising tools” said sean macneill mobilecause ceo “through our engagement platform we have helped thousands of nonprofit organizations communicate effectively with current donors acquire new donors and inspire more recurring donations” additionally mobilecause offers a simple way for fundraisers to set up and promote their own crowdfunding campaign the company recognized the growing interest in crowdfunding and the ability for nonprofits to inspire donors to do more than just give by also encouraging friends family and others to support their cause more and more customers have adopted the crowdfunding feature because it’s flexible enough to maintain a nonprofit’s brand consistency while allowing the individual fundraiser to easily encourage others to donate or participate the platform’s navigation has been restructured to reflect the tasks that are most common for nonprofits when setting up fundraising events and campaigns the user experience now quickly leads them through the platform to more easily accomplish campaign setup execution and followup this usercentric approach is the first step in a line of planned enhancements to better support the urgency in fundraising for nonprofit organizations these product announcements come at a time of increasing acceleration for mobilecause which received a  million investment from level equity earlier this year to learn more visit mobilecausecom   about mobilecause inc mobilecause provides an innovative suite of digital fundraising and donor engagement solutions that help nonprofits do more good with a full suite of customizable mobilefriendly solutions including online forms fundraising events crowdfunding campaign promotion data management and credit card processing with zero transaction fees mobilecause is trusted by thousands of nonprofit organizations including united way the salvation army american heart association university of southern california habitat for humanity and many more attachments a photo accompanying this announcement is available at httpwwwglobenewswirecomnewsroomattachmentngcccedddee kristal bogle mobilecause  kristalmobilecausecom related articles other press releases by mobilecause mobilecause appoints alan park as senior vice president of enterprise sales june    profile mobilecause   subscribe via rss  subscribe via atom  javascript calabasas california united states   httpwwwmobilecausecom contact data kristal bogle mobilecause  kristalmobilecausecom contact with a reader account its easy to send email directly to the contact for this release sign up today for your free reader account already have an account log in here media files mobilecause logo logo url  copy the link below formats available original medium small newswire distribution network  management home newsroom rss feeds legal contact us about us globenewswire a nasdaq company is one of the worlds largest newswire distribution networks specializing in the delivery of corporate press releases financial disclosures and multimedia content to the media investment community individual investors and the general public contact us corporate headquarters  rosecrans avenue suite  el 