e recurring donations”additionally mobilecause offers a simple way for fundraisers to set up and promote their own crowdfunding campaign the company recognized the growing interest in crowdfunding and the ability for nonprofits to inspire donors to do more than just give by also encouraging friends family and others to support their cause more and more customers have adopted the crowdfunding feature because it’s flexible enough to maintain a nonprofit’s brand consistency while allowing the individual fundraiser to easily encourage others to donate or participatethe platform’s navigation has been restructured to reflect the tasks that are most common for nonprofits when setting up fundraising events and campaigns the user experience now quickly leads them through the platform to more easily accomplish campaign setup execution and followup this usercentric approach is the first step in a line of planned enhancements to better support the urgency in fundraising for nonprofit organizationsthese product announcements come at a time of increasing acceleration for mobilecause which received a  million investment from level equity earlier this yearto learn more visit mobilecausecom about mobilecause incmobilecause provides an innovative suite of digital fundraising and donor engagement solutions that help nonprofits do more good with a full suite of customizable mobilefriendly solutions including online forms fundraising events crowdfunding campaign promotion data management and credit card processing with zero transaction fees mobilecause is trusted by thousands of nonprofit organizations including united way the salvation army american heart association university of southern california habitat for humanity and many more attachments a photo accompanying this announcement is available at httpwwwglobenewswirecomnewsroomattachmentngcccedddeekristal boglemobilecausekristalmobilecausecominformation contained on this page is provided by an independent thirdparty content provide