nt donor records and file sharing between countless nonprofit fundraising tools” said sean macneill mobilecause ceo “through our engagement platform we have helped thousands of nonprofit organizations communicate effectively with current donors acquire new donors and inspire more recurring donations” additionally mobilecause offers a simple way for fundraisers to set up and promote their own crowdfunding campaign the company recognized the growing interest in crowdfunding and the ability for nonprofits to inspire donors to do more than just give by also encouraging friends family and others to support their cause more and more customers have adopted the crowdfunding feature because it’s flexible enough to maintain a nonprofit’s brand consistency while allowing the individual fundraiser to easily encourage others to donate or participate the platform’s navigation has been restructured to reflect the tasks that are most common for nonprofits when setting up fundraising events and campaigns the user experience now quickly leads them through the platform to more easily accomplish campaign setup execution and followup this usercentric approach is the first step in a line of planned enhancements to better support the urgency in fundraising for nonprofit organizations these product announcements come at a time of increasing acceleration for mobilecause which received a  million investment from level equity earlier this year to learn more visit mobilecausecom   about mobilecause inc mobilecause provides an innovative suite of digital fundraising and donor engagement solutions that help nonprofits do more good with a full suite of customizable mobilefriendly solutions including online forms fundraising events crowdfunding campaign promotion data management and credit card processing with zero transaction fees mobilecause is trusted by thousands of nonprofit organizations including united way the salvation army american heart association university of southern california habi